headline: The Smartest Dividend Stocks to Buy With $10,000 Right Now
summary: Big tech companies, like Elon Musk's xAI, Microsoft, Meta Platforms, and others, are building out massive data center complexes to tap into the exponentially rising interest in artificial intelligence (AI).  Dell is a major supplier of infrastructure for this xAI project.  Microsoft's server center project in Wisconsin will occupy more than 2 square miles and also use Dell equipment.
